ail vehicle, like, the Support Elon=E2=80=99s Twitter Free Speech Thing Cre=
dit Fund, to buy the debt at 80? Find some buyers who trust Musk completely=
 and don=E2=80=99t want a fight with him.=C2=A0<em>Or</em>, I=E2=80=99d try=
 selling it to Apple Inc., or Jeff Bezos. Selling that debt to someone who =
wants a fight with Musk and can afford it, and who might want to own Twitte=
