rporate trade more efficient. Open to shipping and freight operators, its m=
embers could validate the transaction of goods as recorded on a transparent=
 digital ledger. ...</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CTradeLens has not reached the level o=
