=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0=
00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">
the situation at Redbox Entertainment Inc.</a>, but one possible descriptio=
n is that the board of directors realized it desperately needed to sell its=
elf, and so took a price that was way way lower than its market price.</p>
